| 🔴 Critical | 2 | LINQ chains in hot-path methods; compound allocation chain in Pascalize→Humanize |
| 🟡 Moderate | 4 | `.ToLower()` without culture; `params` array alloc; substring+concat; `Regex.Matches` |
| ℹ️ Info | 1 | Unsealed leaf classes |

